Package com.sun.jimi.core.options

Interface Summary
FormatOptionSet Interface representing a set of options for a format, and methods to dynamically discover them.
 

Class Summary
BasicFormatOptionSet Base class providing partial implementation of the FormatOptionSet interface.
BooleanOption FormatOption for boolean values.
FormatOption Class representing an option for a format.
FormatOptionSetSupport Base class providing partial implementation of the FormatOptionSet interface.
GIFOptions Options class for GIF images.
IntOption FormatOption for int-based values.
JPGOptions Options class for JPG images.
PNGOptions Options class for PNG images.
PSDOptions Options class for Photoshop (PSD) images.
SunRasterOptions Options class for SunRaster images.
 

Exception Summary
OptionException Exception arising due to problems with format-specific options.
